---
/**
 * /ai-stack — PointCast's AI tools best-practices guide.
 *
 * Mike 2026-04-18: "a best practices ai guide, and our current stack
 * what we use, including midjourney, ideogram and any others you can
 * think, deepseek, kimi, runway, etc, tried a bunch and what they are
 * good at."
 *
 * Companion to /stack (which covers the software/infrastructure layer).
 * This one covers AI tools: what we reach for, what each is good at,
 * and when NOT to reach for it.
 *
 * Entries are hand-curated not scraped — this is a POV, not a directory.
 * If you're building something similar, the recommendations are
 * opinionated. Take what's useful, ignore the rest.
 */
